{
  "stem": "1917.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 119.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I ran back to the barrack, and I told Miriam what was happening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she said, well, don't worry so much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We still have a little food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I am so grateful that you're alive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We went to sleep.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We woke up in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You could feel the heat coming through the ceilings, through the walls.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Your-- we looked outside-- the whole sky was red on fire.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The whole camp was on fire.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The same four SS with the jeep were waiting outside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They blew up the remaining gas chambers, crematorium, Canada building, and some of the buildings with-- with as much evidence as they could destroy, and ordered us to march.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The sky was filled with fireworks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I mean, we were the battlefield.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The allies were closing in, and they were fighting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We had to move very fast.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "If we didn't move fast enough, they will shoot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "If-- if you-- if you stayed behind, they would shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So finally, we are-- reached Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "It was 1 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And the four SS disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We raced for the buildings, because we didn't know if they were going to start shooting.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "As we raced for the buildings, I got separated from Miriam.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I got very scared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[SOBBING] I walked 24 hours from building to building.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And luckily, I bumped into her in one doorway.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "There are two sets of twins, two siblings, who had got separated in that same death march, and they still haven't found their sibling twin.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "As I said, we were the battlefield.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We had to tend for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We couldn't find too much food yet.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Most of it was gone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I remember going down one day to the river, because we had no water to drink.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
